<h3><a name="3_5_Installing_and_Configuring_O"></a> 3.5  Installing and Configuring Other Nodes </h3>
<p />
All of these node types and their services are optional, although OSG recommends adding RSV and, for most sites, the Frontier Squid caching service.
<p /> <ul>
<li> RSV monitoring to monitor and report to OSG on the health of your site <ul>
<li> <span class="twikiNewLink">RSV Overview<a href="/bin/edit/Sandbox/RsvOverview?topicparent=Sandbox.InstallOverview" rel="nofollow" title="RSV Overview (this topic does not yet exist; you can create it)">?</a></span>
